headline: Keepr.Co Closes $400,000 Crowdfund, surpassing $1.3 Million in Total Funding
summary: LONDON, Sept. 23, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Keepr, also known as kitkeeper.co.uk, represents a digitally-led alternative to conventional self-storage solutions. Utilising a platform with a network of logistics and warehouse providers, Keepr facilitates the delivery of storage boxes, the collection of packed items, and their secure storage until retrieval is required. Positioned as the ‘Airbnb for storage’, the company has successfully raised over $1.3 million, including $400,000 through crowdfund
